# 9. Generate Alerts

## Large Ping

From Kali:

```bash
ping -s 200 192.168.74.10
```

Alert:

```text
ICMP Packet >128 Bytes
```

---

## ICMP Flood

```bash
for i in {1..50}
do
ping -c 1 192.168.74.10
done
```

Alert:

```text
ICMP Flood Detected
```

---

## SYN Flood

Install:

```bash
sudo apt install hping3 -y
```

Run:

```bash
sudo hping3 -S -p 80 --flood 192.168.74.10
```

Alert:

```text
SYN Flood Against Web Server
```

---

## SSH Brute Force

Install:

```bash
sudo apt install hydra -y
```

Run:

```bash
hydra -l root -P rockyou.txt ssh://192.168.74.10
```

Alert:

```text
SSH Brute Force Attack
```

---

## Kali Detection

Renew DHCP:

```bash
sudo dhclient -r
sudo dhclient
```

Alert:

```text
Kali Linux Boot Detected
```

---

